title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 12 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: The media establishment is all-in on pressuring Florida and especially Governor DeSantis to bend the knee. There must be much we're not being told about covid spread; the data doesn't explain it. Data once again shows that covid fear about kids is overblown. The school mask rebellion is underway in some places. How many covid breakthrough cases are there right now? The Taliban will control Afghanistan before the summer ends. How did the U.S. fail so badly in Afghanistan?
